_______________________________________________________________________________
__ SYPNOSIS ___________________________________________________________________

The luawrap component provides the C++ LuaClass wrapper for lua classes. 

_______________________________________________________________________________
__ USAGE ______________________________________________________________________

To create a LuaClass object one needs to subclass LuaClass in the following 
way: 

class SomeClass: public LuaClass {

public:

  SomeClass(const LuaContext& context) : LuaClass(context) { ... }

  ...
};


To instantiate the class one first needs to create the context:

LuaContext context; 

SomeClass aclass(context);

